metadata.name: BIG Monkey #1
metadata.description: NFT of Earth Power - one of the 8 different Powers of the 1st BIG Monkeys collection “Money Generation” of rare 888 NFTs with passive income. BIG Monkeys with Earth Power know everything from mining gold to metaagriculture. For sure, the key factor is hard work. As long as you work hard, coins keep on pouring. If you don’t, save the drama for your mama. Not everyone here is subject to great ideas and missions, but there are many happy, kind BIG Monkeys. After all, if you want to make money on land, you have to love it.
